Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(座敷童子)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(前篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣很擋路耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人會進不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找別人跟你買藥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住一晚！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(睽違已久)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的月光照着你徘徊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的話卻說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶記那虛偽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻那溫暖的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有如失了魂的空虛眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的下弦月隱臟在雲間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述說着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱着孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚只能夠幽幽嘆息嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(當晚)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子…你很冷吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很苦吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是中藥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘\N您獨自經營這家旅館嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房子\N在我很年輕的時候就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在改成旅館之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是做什麼的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀大了不記得了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我借宿一晚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我們已經打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請去別家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這附近還亮着燈的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是已經客滿了啦！\N拜託您哪裡都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算讓我睡泥巴地也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！加上你就客滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼~這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我…正被人追殺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被發現…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會沒命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳越講越扯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妳這麼年輕漂亮的姑娘\N好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面淋雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐人膏又名半助膏藥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很可憐啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續淋雨的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子裡的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會流產的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳懷孕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~真是的真聽不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德次你都站幾年櫃台了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉！我們不想惹麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳快點出去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦走出這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走出這裡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會在這家店的門口…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺着我跟腹中胎兒的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是更麻煩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會被妳威脅的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有威脅您！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何\N我都要生下這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就無法保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德次，過來\N老闆娘拜託您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我求您好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她帶到那個房間去\N求求您行行好！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼~那個房間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶她到房間去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去把被子準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…非常謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明讓她睡我房間也是可以的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間平常是不安排客人住的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外人也不知道有這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請妳無論如何安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子有點餓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能給我點東西吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在惡作劇啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了…明天再叫德次清掉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一些飯糰喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經這麼晚了說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下就有東西吃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那麼想把孩子生下來啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不清楚是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳打算獨自撫養他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確有這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了只能說妳太年輕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想法比較天真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嬰兒不是只要吃飯就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的出生不受祝福\N妳又硬把他生下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時為了養活他遇到困難\N對那孩子來說好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要生下這個孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的年輕人真是固執啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的話才不會…\N老闆娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這麼不負責任的事喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被單應該就快送過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得幫妳準備飯糰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您…老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倒翁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀~賣藥的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去廁所的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那個走廊轉個彎就到了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面也有房間？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能不過是倉庫而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別自已跑上去喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~剛剛買藥的錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係明天再給也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先告辭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底掉到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是從哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我還給我還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳懷了小寶寶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再四個月就會從這裡出來喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳很開心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯當然開心囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂~我們去那邊好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦！倒是你快點回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…放過我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳如果生了男孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後又厚着臉皮出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺跟夫人…會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟少爺分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管妳這個\N不懂人情世故的女人講什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想把孩子生下來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都到這裡了\N怎麼能空手而回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃\N這個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧！\N這個孩子希望出生到這世上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三更半夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵什麼吵啊…真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裡？\N這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你幹的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪老闆娘讓她住這房間\N保護她嗎？可是…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德次！你去報警！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會沒必要？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個人被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而殺死他的人是你…\N不是這個人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手…不是這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被捲住往上飛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是上面什麼都沒有，然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉轉轉轉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉轉轉轉啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你怎麼會在這個房間？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手…並不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自已打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個賣藥的\N怎麼會帶這麼噁心的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了斬殺喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬、斬什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是物怪喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有被什麼纏住的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡說八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看這個屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情人類是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡怎麼會有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打哪兒來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就擺在房裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有個孩子過來拿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在胡說些什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚沒有帶着孩子的客人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那些腳步聲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有笑聲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘帶我來這房間的時候\N也有聽到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也沒聽到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽有這麼多孩子的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽那邊也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底在胡說什麼\N這裡是頂樓喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更裡面的房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊也有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟這房間有關聯的物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩嬰兒的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是座敷童子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拔出退魔劍是有條件的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果無法找出“形”、“真”、“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼劍就無法拔出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪的“形”\N是基於人的淵源跟因果形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真”乃事情的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”乃心的樣貌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道各位的真與理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:21:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請仔細道來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待續)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法笑得開懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在隨處可見的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些無可取代的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能夠好好珍惜地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已經別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:22:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛開在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨風緩緩飄落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在那早已看不見的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子也令人珍愛到無可比喻
